{"tid":1811744,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[找數時間] 民間集會團隊「12.23星火不息集會」財務報告","createTime":"2020-01-05T03:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T07:52:25.000Z","uid":42194,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc26c6d69339f30bf3b883a6bcb70ce6cf4b8db","tid":1811744,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"首先要講聲唔好意思<br />\n因為是次活動籌備時間傖拙，又活動完之後緊接住聖誕新年一系列活動<br />\n所以埋數埋得遲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再次感謝各位手足，響之前嘅12 月 23日，約45000 人去到愛丁堡廣場參加「星火不息，燃點國際」集會，民間集會團隊再次感謝各位在工作日晚上抽空出席集會，亦感謝音樂人工會讓出場地，讓愛丁堡廣場能再現星海，支援星火。<br />\n<br />\n現奉上 12.23「星火不息，燃點國際」集會的財務報告：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCGttLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCGttLW.jpg&h=526f19af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n財務報告亦已載於我地於collaction 嘅專頁之中： <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/objective/5110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2FHKCATeam%2Fobjective%2F5110&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=cd56e27b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/objective/5110</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊<br />\nFacebook <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=ec456542\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam</a><br />\nInstagram <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkcat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkcat%2F&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=1980b535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkcat/</a><br />\nTwitter <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKCATeam&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLTBOARg6